---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import meImage from '../assets/image3.jpg';
---

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jeffrey Chang</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/5c24dc808e.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        h1 {
            font-weight: lighter;
            font-size: xx-large;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        h3 {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            grid-column: span 2;
            color: #b0b0b0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #1f1f1f;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #3c00b3;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .image-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .rounded-image {
            max-width: 17em;
            max-height: 21em;
            border-radius: 10px;
            object-fit: contain;
            margin: 1%;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .rounded-image:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .text-container {
            max-width: 30em;
            background-color: #1f1f1f;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .my-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        #contact {
            background-color: #1f1f1f;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            color: #b0b0b0;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
        }

        #contact h2 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        #contact a {
            color: #3c00b3;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 1rem;
        }

        #contact a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .image-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .rounded-image {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }

        .fade-out {
            animation: fadeOut 350ms ease;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        @keyframes fadeOut {
            from { opacity: 1; }
            to { opacity: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Jeffrey Chang</h1>
    <h3>Welcome to one of the websites of all time!</h3>
    <a href="/cv" class="button">View My CV</a>

    <div class="image-container">
        <Image src={meImage} alt="An image of meeee" class="rounded-image" />
        <div class="text-container">
            <p>Helloooo! I am a student studying Information and Communication Technology with an interest in project management. Welcome to my website!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="my-grid">
        <div>
            I'm currently studying my fourth year at KTH Royal Institute of Technology in Stockholm.
            It's the Swedish 5-year program called "Civilingenj√∂r",
            which is the equivalent to a bachelors and masters in engineering degree!
        </div>
        <div>
            I have an interest in both project management and programming.
            Outside of school, I like to spend my time in non-profit engagements. A majority of my time
            goes to the Student Union by, for example, being the Project Manager of
            <a href="https://www.armada.nu" target="_blank" class="armada"> THS Armada</a>!
        </div>
        <div>
            But back to the IT stuff. I have taken a lot of backend and frontend programming courses, and while I can do both,
            I have more of an interest in frontend and app development!
            I have also taken way too many maths courses and some leadership courses as well :D
        </div>
        <div>
            Now, if you are interested in what you have read so far, I have a fantastic LinkedIn and Email,
            at the bottom of the page, for you to contact me with more details about me and what I do!
            You can also find my CV and previous projects on this website!
        </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/projects" class="button">Projects</a>

    <div id="contact">
        <h2>Reach out to me at:</h2>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/zwjc" target="_blank">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin fa-xl"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:zw.jchang@gmail.com">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope fa-xl"></i>
        </a>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const transitionLinks = document.querySelectorAll('a.button');

            transitionLinks.forEach(link => {
                link.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    document.body.classList.add('fade-out');

                    setTimeout(() => {
                        window.location.href = this.getAttribute('href');
                    }, 350);
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
